quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaaf-Ha-Ya-Aiin-Sād (K. H. Y. I. S). [Bachi gaŋ gaŋ ŋɔ maa wuhirimi ni Alkur’aani nyɛla Muɣujizah (lahiʒibsi din ka ŋmali), dama so ʒi di fasara naɣila Naawuni"
  19,2,(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Ŋɔ maa nyɛla teebu n-zaŋ chaŋ a Duuma (Naawuni) ni daa zo O dabli Annabi Zakariya nambɔɣu shεm
  19,3,Saha shεli o (Annabi Zakariya) ni daa boli o Duuma (Naawuni) boondi shεli din nyɛ sɔɣisinli ni
  19,4,"Ka o (Annabi Zakariya) yεli: “Yaa n Duuma (Naawuni)! Achiiika! Gbarginsim paai ma, ka n zabri palgi. M-mi pala A ni zaɣisiri so suhigu deebu.”"
  19,5,"“Yaha! Achiika! N-zɔrila n dɔɣim dabiɛm n kum nyaaŋa, ka m paɣa mi nyɛ paɣaŋɔli, dinzuɣu tim ma bisuŋ ŋun yi A sani na.”"
  19,6,"“Ka o di n fali, ka di Annabi Ya’akuba yiŋnim’ fali. Yaha! Zaŋmi o leei a ni niŋ so yεda.”"
  19,7,"(Ka Naawuni yɛli): “Yaa nyini Zakariya! Achiika! Ti tiri a suhupiεlli lahibali ni bidibbila so (a paɣa ni yɛn dɔɣi), ka o yuli yɛn nyɛ “Yahaya.” Ti na ʒin zaŋ yuli ŋɔ maa m-boli ninvuɣu so pɔi ni ŋuna.”"
  19,8,"Ka o (Annabi Zakaria) yεli: “Yaa n Duuma (Naawuni)! N-yɛn niŋ wula mali bia, ka m paɣa nyɛ paɣaŋɔli, ka n kuriginsim lahi paai tariga"
  19,9,"Ka o (Malaaika) yεli: “Lala ka a Duuma (Naawuni) yεli, di nyɛla soochi N (Mani Naawuni) sani. Achiika! N-daa nam a mi ka a pa shɛli.”"
  19,10,"Ka o (Annabi Zakariya) yεli: “Yaa n Duuma! Wuhimi ma alaama shεli (din wuhiri ni m paɣa ni dɔɣi), ka o (Naawuni) yεli: “A daalaama nyɛla a ku tooi tɔɣisi yɛltɔɣa ni niriba dabsa ata, ka kuli nyɛla ŋun mali alaafee.”"
  19,11,"Ka o (Annabi Zakariya) yi o niriba sani o jεma shee n-ti tiri wuhi ba (ka yεli): “Niŋmi ya Naawuni kasi Asiba ni Zaawuni.”"